open-lmake ($VERSION_TAG-$DEBIAN_RELEASE) $OS_CODENAME; urgency=low

  * General clean up release

  * implement ConfigRule to handle configs in a lmake-friendly way
  * handle $NO_COLOR
  * improve regexpr matching perf
  * improve lshow -i by providing more information
  * improve slurm scheduling by passing it timeout info
  * support ubuntu26.04 and gcc-15
  * bug fixes
  * improved error messages
  * improve perf

 -- Cesar Douady <cesar.douady@doliam.fr>  $DATE
